reviewText: I bought this triple feature cause I was looking for Men at Work for the longest time. I had no idea about NO MAN'S LAND or NAVY SEALS. After watching NAVY SEALS, I must say that is a great action packed movie with a terrific story line. NO MAN'S LAND is also good as well. MEN AT WORK is still one of my all time favorite comedies but I would recommend to any potential buyer to seek out this triple feature so that you can grab three great movies for a great price.
If your a charlie fan this a a great dvd for anyone , it was a great deal because i was looking for  just one of thease and ended up with three great movies .
